data.name: RichTextBox_video.Text
data.value:
The steps to complete the analysis are: •Create and save the ADINA macro. •Open ADINA-AUI. •Select open from the File menu. •Select ADINA-AUI Session Files from Files of Types in the new dialog window. •navigate to the location where the macro was saved and select it •if all the modeling steps (model, BC, Load and mesh generation) were performed, the user can run the FE analysis to obtain results. •After the analysis was perfore, select the ADINA-PLOT to draw the results by opening the results file.
Pressing the image on the left opens a wmv file which demonstrate the process.

data.name: RichTextBox_welcome.Text
data.value:
Welcome to ADINA Generator. This module create ADINA Session file (*.ses) with ADINA 8.1 syntax.
The module currently has the following limitations :
•The Plate must have at least one stiffener in each axis. •All the stiffeners have the same height but the thicknesses can vary (so to achieve different moments of inertia). •The lateral load is uniform pressure acting on the plate itself. •The type of elements for the stiffeners and plate is SHELL ONLY. The shell parameter can be change by the user.
